  initialDialog:
  - "The sun has set, and the shadows are moving... Do you hear \uADF8 squishing
    sound?"
  - Slimes! They are drawn to the warmth of our camp. They look weak, but they'll
    wear you down if you're not careful.
  - Use your Stone Axe to fend them off. If you get hurt, remember we still have
    some bread in the emergency rations.
